Class TypeAttributeAppender.ForAnnotation

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bytebuddy.implementation.attribute.TypeAttributeAppender.ForAnnotation

    TypeAttributeAppender

    TypeAttributeAppender

    public static class TypeAttributeAppender.ForAnnotation
extends Object
implements TypeAttributeAppender
    An attribute appender that appends a single annotation to a given type. The visibility for the annotation will be inferred from the annotation's RetentionPolicy.
